ZH: 这个药已经停产了，你可以尝试找寻其他代替品。
EN: This medicine has been discontinued, you can try to find an alternative product.

ZH: 在缺货的情况下，我们会尽力为你提供代替品。
EN: In the case of out-of-stock, we will do our best to provide you with a substitute.

ZH: 有些人对乳制品过敏，他们可以寻找代替品。
EN: Some people are allergic to dairy products, they can look for alternatives.

ZH: 如果这个牌子的酱料卖完了，你可以试试其他代替品。
EN: If this brand of sauce is sold out, you can try other alternatives.

ZH: 这个电子产品有不同的代替品可供选择。
EN: There are different alternatives for this electronic product to choose from.

ZH: 受伤的猫咪需要手术，但是手术器械已经用完，需要找个代替品。
EN: The injured cat needs surgery, but the surgical instruments are out of stock, we need to find an alternative.

ZH: 这种食品有更健康和低卡路里的代替品。
EN: There are healthier and lower-calorie alternatives to this type of food.

ZH: 他担心这个原料可能会引起过敏，因此他正在寻找代替品。
EN: He is worried that this ingredient may cause an allergy, so he is looking for a substitute.

ZH: 这个细胞培养基的配方需要更稳定的代替品。
EN: The formula for this cell culture medium needs a more stable alternative.

ZH: 饭菜中的盐被替换成了低钠代替品。
EN: Salt in the food has been replaced with a low-sodium alternative.

ZH: 由于紧缺，我们只能提供你一个代替品。
EN: Due to the shortage, we can only provide you with one alternative.

ZH: 糖尿病人需要选择无糖的代替品。
EN: Diabetics need to choose sugar-free alternatives.

ZH: 这个零食有了新的口味代替品。
EN: This snack has a new flavor substitute.

ZH: 这种化妆品的成分被证明有害，需要寻找更安全的代替品。
EN: The ingredients of this cosmetic have proven to be harmful, need to find a safer alternative.

ZH: 我们将为每位员工提供工作在家的代替品。
EN: We will provide telecommuting alternatives for each employee.

ZH: 这款游戏的暴力内容受到批评，需要找到适合的代替品。
EN: The violent content of this game is criticized and needs to find a suitable alternative.

ZH: 食材店中的某些食物因季节性原因缺货，我们正在寻找代替品。
EN: Some food in the ingredient store is out of stock due to seasonal reasons, and we are looking for alternatives.

ZH: 这个洗发水的易泡沫配方已经停产，我们需要替换为代替品。
EN: The easy foaming formula of this shampoo has been discontinued, and we need to replace it with an alternative.

ZH: 这个医学实验用的试剂耗尽了，需要购买代替品。
EN: The reagents used in this medical experiment have been exhausted, and alternatives need to be purchased.

ZH: 这道菜的调味料有更健康的替代品可供选择。
EN: There are healthier substitutes for the seasonings in this dish.
